RHVoice is a free and open source speech synthesizer.
It consists of the following components:

 - command line tool `rhvoice-client` (needs love)
 - speech module for NVDA
 - speech module for Windows (SAPI5)
 - Android App

See downloads at https://github.com/Olga-Yakovleva/RHVoice/wiki/Downloads

Source code for development version can be fetched with git from:

    git://github.com/Olga-Yakovleva/RHVoice.git
